Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.55,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Arima…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.69,0:21:45.06,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Sacó varias canciones\Naparte de "Piiman Taisou".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.28,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,No tenía ni idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.74,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,-¿Quieres escucharla?\N-Claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:54.25,Cart_A_Tre,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,938)\c&HFFFEFF&\bord0\fsp1\fs12\pos(523.261,248.626)}Kana Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.41,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,Es una chica muy complicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.05,Gen_Main,,0,0,0,,¿Y dice que canta mal?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.97,Cart_A_Verd,CARTEL,0,0,0,,{\shad\fs40\c&H5F00E2&\bord7\3c&H2EFFFA&\1a&HFF&\pos(565.715,49.713)}Puntos
